flowchart LR
    subgraph build [Build]
        direction TB
        Checkout[Checkout Code] --> Install[Install Dependencies]
        Install --> Compile[Compile]
        Compile --> Test[Run Tests]
    end
    subgraph deploy [Deploy]
        direction TB
        Package[Package Artifact] --> Stage[Deploy to Staging]
        Stage --> Verify[Run Smoke Tests]
